        {
            "title": "尖沙咀凱譽 寬闊廳堂空間感強 設開放式廚房",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"尖沙咀凱譽 寬闊廳堂空間感強 設開放式廚房\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/43b9d7222788731985148b46c9747643/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250410/_2025041016073246364.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">尖沙咀凱譽 寬闊廳堂空間感強 設開放式廚房</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>尖沙咀繁華且交通網絡完善，其中的單幢盤凱譽更是坐落核心地段，配套完善。今日介紹該廈低層D室，實用面積349方呎，1房間隔，內附靚裝，入住方便，現以月租30000元放租，實用呎租約86元。\n\n</p>\n<p>走進單位，見廳堂牆身髹上藍色系，鋪設灰色雲石地磚，已將沙發、飯桌及收納櫃等整齊擺放，住客可即租即住。廳內備有闊窗，通風光亮。\n\n</p>\n<p>放盤設有1間房，房間皆四正實用，其中的房內見已配置牀具及衣櫃等。浴室方面，潔具齊備，採乾濕分離的設計。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4187772/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"客飯廳布置講究，可即時入住。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/22afcc22a08b703de62ac419e8094668/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_10_04_29_AM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        客飯廳布置講究，可即時入住。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4187773/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"浴室潔具新淨，亦有不少儲物空間。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ccea67c377c4194b2e2ae5044ce3ad5a/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_10_04_29_AM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        浴室潔具新淨，亦有不少儲物空間。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4187774/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"廚房設備齊全，有多組儲物廚櫃。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/02b0f731e511190c3ad50e51e9a52eb4/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_10_04_29_AM_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        廚房設備齊全，有多組儲物廚櫃。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4187775/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"尖沙咀凱譽低層D室，實用面積349方呎，以月租30000元招租。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bc295c5a54a52f874536ba28fc113ec1/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_10_04_29_AM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        尖沙咀凱譽低層D室，實用面積349方呎，以月租30000元招租。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4187777/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"尖沙咀凱譽外貌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb71c5bc8259110beab2ed24b97592b2/2025-04/PC240715PINNACLE059_2_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        尖沙咀凱譽外貌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>349方呎1房間隔</h2>\n<p>由恒基發展的凱譽，樓齡約24年，共提供262伙，會所備連戶外泳池、健身室、高爾夫球練習場等。\n\n</p>\n<p>牆身以雲石紋為主，配以充足光線，明亮又整潔。廚房採用開放式設計，廚櫃以深啡色為主調，易於打理。另安裝有焗爐、電磁爐具等，迎合下廚人士的基本需要。\n\n</p>\n<p>配套方面，與物業一街之隔即為港鐵尖東站，接通中環線。咫尺亦為K11等大型商場，購物及日常所需一應俱全。\n\n</p><h2>必睇靚位</h2>\n<p>位於尖沙咀核心地帶\n\n</p>\n<p>連品味裝潢\n\n</p>\n<p>四正開則，方便布置\n\n</p>\n<p>鄰近港鐵尖東站\n\n</p><h2>放盤單位資料 </h2>\n<p>物業名稱：凱譽\n\n</p>\n<p>地址：棉登徑8號\n\n</p>\n<p>樓齡：23年\n\n</p>\n<p>單位：低層D室\n\n</p>\n<p>實用面積：349方呎\n\n</p>\n<p>間隔：1房\n\n</p>\n<p>叫租：30000元\n\n</p>\n<p>呎租：86元\n\n</p>\n<p>代理行：香港置業\n\n</p>\n<p>電話：6290 3930（Ann Ho）\n\n</p>\n<p>*相片由代理行提供\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063211/即時-地產-尖沙咀凱譽-寬闊廳堂空間感強-設開放式廚房",
